The General Administration of Market Supervision recently issued the Notice on Strengthening Market Price Supervision during the National Day of the Mid-Autumn Festival in 2018, which calls for strengthening price supervision in the field of housing rental and real estate, cracking down on price violations such as collusion in rent prices, hoarding rental housing sources, fabricating false information to inflate rents, charging fees by means of bundled services, publishing misleading price information and not clearly marking prices.
The notice is clear that we should strengthen price monitoring and early warning and pay close attention to market price dynamics.
All localities should pay close attention to the necessities of life such as high consumption of grain, oil, meat, poultry, eggs, vegetables and milk salt, as well as the market and price changes of special commodities consumed by local residents during the holidays, and strengthen price monitoring and analysis and early warning.
Once the tendentious and seedling problems of market fluctuations are found, timely measures are taken to defuse them effectively.
We should strengthen the supervision and inspection of the wholesale and retail links of necessities of life, increase the frequency and supervision of places closely related to the daily consumption of the masses, such as the commercial super-market and the farmers' market, and urge operators to operate in accordance with the law and in good faith.
The notice pointed out that inspection in key areas should be strengthened to create a good holiday consumption environment; the supervision of ticket prices in state-owned scenic spots should be strengthened; emphasis should be placed on investigating and dealing with illegal and illegal acts such as non-implementation of the price level or floating range set by the government in state-owned scenic spots, unauthorized addition of fee items, disguised increase in ticket prices through the illegal establishment of "garden" tickets, high pricing and large discounts, bundled sales, failure to price clearly in accordance with the regulations, non-implementation of preferential measures, extra-price increases and compulsory collection of fees.
The notice calls for strengthening the supervision of the price of necessities of life, especially agricultural products.
Affected by seasonal changes, natural disasters and outbreaks, the prices of essential agricultural products such as vegetables and pork have recently fluctuated in some areas.
All localities should, in the light of the actual local situation, effectively strengthen the supervision of market prices for agricultural and by-product products, cooperate with the relevant departments in stabilizing production and market supply, and organize efforts to carry out key market inspections and random spot checks.
We will increase the frequency of inspection of pork and other commodities with tight supply and rapid price increases, and seriously investigate and deal with illegal acts such as hoarding, price-raising and collusion in price increases.
The notice states that price supervision in the housing rental and real estate sectors should be strengthened.
The Mid-Autumn Festival and the National Day coincide with the peak season for the sale of housing rental and commercial housing. All localities should pay close attention to the price behavior of real estate enterprises, intermediary companies and housing rental-related enterprises, crack down on price violations such as collusion in rent prices, hoarding of rental housing sources, fabricating and hype false information to inflate rents, charging fees by means of bundled services, publishing misleading price information and not clearly marking prices, increase the inspection of the price situation of hot-selling properties and real estate agents on sale, and investigate and deal with the failure to implement "one set of one standard" in accordance with the regulations to disrupt the order of the real estate market, purify the real estate market, and create an open and transparent price order of the real estate market.
The notice mentioned that all localities should do a good job in price supervision of other links in the tourism industry, focus on standardizing the price order of catering, accommodation, shopping, sightseeing, entertainment and parking, guide operators to do a good job in the public announcement of prices and fees, and seriously investigate and deal with all kinds of price violations.
The notice said it was necessary to strengthen the inspection of transport prices such as roads, railways, civil aviation and water transport, and to seriously investigate and deal with illegal acts such as illegal price increases, out-of-price tolls and non-clear pricing in accordance with the regulations.
We will implement the "green channel" for the transport of fresh agricultural products and the policy of waiving tolls for small passenger cars on major holidays.
We should innovate regulatory means and working methods, strengthen the publicity of price laws and regulations for online and offline commodity retail enterprises and e-commerce platforms, urge operators to improve price promotion plans, and investigate and deal with illegal acts such as fictitious original prices, misleading price tags and non-compliance with price commitments in accordance with the law.
