The portion paid abroad does not require personal income tax to be paid within China.
The Ministry of Finance, the State Administration of Taxation, the National Development and Reform Commission and the Ministry of Commerce of China have also issued a notice to expand the scope of application of the policy of temporary non-collection of advance income tax for direct investment by overseas investors in the distribution of profits.
