In response to the incident of "a primary school student in Suining being corporal punishment by a teacher for doing the wrong question", the official microblog of the Heidong New District Management Committee of Suining City issued a briefing yesterday saying that after investigation, Luo XX, a teacher at Suzhou Foreign Languages Primary School, had been transferred from his post as a teacher and the school involved had been disqualified from the annual "evaluation".
