This newspaper news (intern reporter Li Qiyao) in recent years, many places have occurred the campus plastic runway substandard incident.
To this end, the Ministry of Education issued a notice requiring the new national standard to be implemented at the surface-level sports venues for synthetic materials in primary and secondary schools that are delivered for use after 1 November this year.
The mandatory national standard, "Surface Sports Ground for Synthetic Materials in Primary and Secondary Schools", was led by the Ministry of Education and drafted with the participation of 26 scientific research institutes and testing institutions. After more than two years of revision, more than 100 expert meetings were organized during the period, as well as field visits and sample inspections throughout the country, and countless verification experiments of the products of hundreds of enterprises on the market were collected.
In contrast to the old national standard in 2005, the reporter found that the new national standard not only changed from the "National Recommended Standard" to the "National Compulsory Standard", but also added a lot of content, including thickness requirements, physical properties, aging resistance, inorganic packing content requirements, anti-skid rubber polymer content requirements, limit of harmful substances for finished products on the surface layer, and limit of harmful substances for non-solid and solid raw materials.
In particular, it is worth mentioning that the new national standard limits the number of harmful substances that may be produced in the construction of plastic runways on campus, from 7 to 18, and sets out the limit of volatile organic matter on the completed runway in accordance with the home furnishings standards.
For example, the release of harmful substances is clearly stipulated in the Limits and Odour Requirements for Hazardous Substances in Cast-in-situ and Prefabricated Surface Products, requiring that total volatile organic compounds should not be higher than 5 mg / m3, formaldehyde should not be higher than 0.4 mg / m3, carbon disulfide should not be higher than 7 mg / m3, benzene should not be higher than 0.1 mg / m3 and the odour level should not be higher than 3.
The new national standard also makes detailed provisions on the sampling requirements, inspection rules and determination rules of plastic runways in primary and secondary schools.
In addition, the campus artificial lawn is also included in the scope of compulsory testing of the national standard for the first time.
In the near future, all localities will carry out special work arrangements on the implementation of the new national standard, and report the implementation of the new national standard to the Department of Physical Health and Arts Education of the Ministry of Education during the year.
China New Network client Chengdu September 30 (Wang Yu) 30 afternoon, the 2018 women's table tennis World Cup final arena staged the "national table tennis civil war".
In the end, Grand Slam winner Ding Ning beat home team-mate Zhu Yuling 4-0 to reach the women's table tennis World Cup title again after four years, the 21st time the Chinese women's table tennis team has won the tournament.
Ding Ning and Zhu Yuling are team-mates and friends, both sides are quite familiar with each other's skills and tactics.
Whether preparing for the war or pre-match warm-up, both sides followed suit.
Entering the final, the two men said they had completed the task of the match.
But the contest between Ding Ning and Zhu Yuling in the competition, can be called a knife and sword.
In the first set, Ding Ning, who had the dominant experience in the competition, took a 3-1 lead at the start, and then Zhu Yuling took advantage of Ding Ning's mistake to tie the score at 3.
Then Zhu Yuling's mistakes in the attack began to increase, and Ding Ning took the opportunity to take a 3-point 9-5 lead in a row and take the lead 10-6 to get the game point.
Although Zhu Yuling chased three points in a row, but Ding Ning used his serve to take the first set 11-9.
In the second set, Zhu Yuling's mistakes remained high, and Ding Ning took a 6-1 lead with the advantage of holding each other.
Zhu Yuling, who trailed 2-7, relied on a rhythm change to score two points in a row, and then used the attack to chase the score to 8-9 at one point.
At the crucial moment, Ding Ning scored 2 points 11-8 to win another set.
In the third set, the two men got off to a tight start to draw 3-3.
Ding Ning then made more mistakes in the attack and lost three points in a row, but she then used a sharp attack to score three points in a row to tie the score at 6.
Zhu Yuling scored 2 points in a row to establish the advantage again, and took the lead with 10: 8 to get the game point.
But Ding Ning's attack was extremely fierce, scoring four points in a row before taking the third set at 12:10.
In the 4th set, Zhu Yuling started to take a 4-2 lead.
But since then Ding Ning has shown a super-strong offensive state, scoring four points in a row after stopping Zhu Yuling.
After the suspension back, Zhu Yuling recovered some form and gradually chased the score to an 8-8 draw.
At the crucial moment, Ding Ning did not have a soft hand, scored 2 points in a row to get the match point.
With Zhu Yuling back to the ball out of bounds, Ding Ning swept his opponent 4-0 to win the title.
Last month, Ding Ning won the Bulgarian Open, ending her 14-month title drought, and this time she came to Chengdu, although she said before the match that she had not set a target for the tournament, while in the semi-finals, which ended in the morning, Ding Ning said she had completed her task.
In the end, Ding Ning beat team-mate Zhu Yuling to win her third World Cup title, and she expressed satisfaction with her performance: "A champion is important to every athlete.
Before the match, I didn't expect this, just said a game to fight, the final itself is still very satisfied. "
Zhu Yuling, a sister of Sichuan who fought at home, won a silver medal and did not complete her goal of defending her title. Speaking about whether the enthusiastic crowd at home would put invisible pressure on herself, she said: "I think I can deal with the whole game in terms of pressure. Today Ding Ning played very well, so that she has not found a rhythm."
Activating rural consumption, we should rely on the normal mechanism to purify the market, guide the demand for healthy consumption, and enhance the sense of farmers' consumption.
According to the data, the consumption potential of rural residents continued to be released, with retail sales of rural consumer goods up 10.5% in the first half of this year, 1.3%age points higher than in cities and towns.
During a visit to a poverty-stricken village in a western county, there was only one convenience store in the village. Walking into the store, some goods were familiar. "Golden Dragon Fish" was marked "Golden Dragon Oil", "Wangzi" became "Wangmilk" and "shanzhai" commodities were many.
